Feature: User can register
	- User cannot register unless he/she has valid email credentials
	- No other informations is required
	- User can continue to browse the website without registration

Feature: User can login
	- User cannot login unless he/she has registered
	- User does not login until button is pressed
	- Password are not displayed during login
	- Usernames will be displayed during login
	- User is notified of login upon completion
